@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry / User starts creating account
CreateAccount : do / Fill details
CreateAccount : exit / Account created

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry / User starts watching videos
WatchVideos : do / Watch videos
WatchVideos : exit / User stops watching

state "Upload Videos" as UploadVideos
UploadVideos : entry / User starts uploading videos
UploadVideos : do / Upload videos
UploadVideos : exit / Videos uploaded

state "Save Videos" as SaveVideos
SaveVideos : entry / User saves videos
SaveVideos : do / Add to likes list
SaveVideos : exit / Videos saved

state "View Likes List" as ViewLikesList
ViewLikesList : entry / User views saved videos
ViewLikesList : do / View saved videos
ViewLikesList : exit / User finishes viewing

state "Enter Discussion" as EnterDiscussion
EnterDiscussion : entry / User enters discussion
EnterDiscussion : do / Participate in discussion
EnterDiscussion : exit / User exits discussion

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos : [After creating account]
CreateAccount --> UploadVideos : [After creating account]
CreateAccount --> SaveVideos : [After creating account]
CreateAccount --> ViewLikesList : [After creating account]
CreateAccount --> EnterDiscussion : [After creating account]

WatchVideos --> [*] : [User stops watching]

UploadVideos --> [*] : [User stops uploading]

SaveVideos --> ViewLikesList : [User wants to view saved videos]

ViewLikesList --> [*] : [User finishes viewing]

EnterDiscussion --> [*] : [User exits discussion]

@enduml
